<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=List_of_writing_systems&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4" title="Edit section: Syllable-based logographies">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Syllable-based logographies</span></h3>
