<li><b><a href="/wiki/Yi_script#Classical_Yi" title="Yi script">Yi</a> (classical)</b>&#160;– various <a href="/wiki/Yi_language" title="Yi language" class="mw-redirect">Yi/Lolo languages</a></li>
