<li><b><a href="/wiki/Tai_Tham_script" title="Tai Tham script">Tai Tham</a></b>&#160;– <a href="/w/index.php?title=Kh%C3%BCn_language&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Khün language (page does not exist)">Khün</a>, and <a href="/wiki/Northern_Thai_language" title="Northern Thai language">Northern Thai</a></li>
<li><b><a href="/wiki/Tamil_script" title="Tamil script">Tamil</a></b></li>
<li><b><a href="/wiki/Telugu_script" title="Telugu script">Telugu</a></b></li>
<li><b><a href="/wiki/Thai_alphabet" title="Thai alphabet">Thai</a></b></li>
