<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=List_of_writing_systems&amp;action=edit&amp;section=22" title="Edit section: Other">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Other</span></h2>
<p><a name="Phonetic_alphabets" id="Phonetic_alphabets"></a></p>
