<li><a href="http://www.ancientscripts.com/ws.html" class="external text" title="http://www.ancientscripts.com/ws.html" rel="nofollow">Ancient Scripts: Home</a>(Site with some introduction to different writing systems and group them into <a href="http://www.ancientscripts.com/ws_types.html" class="external text" title="http://www.ancientscripts.com/ws_types.html" rel="nofollow">origins</a>/<a href="http://www.ancientscripts.com/ws_types.html" class="external text" title="http://www.ancientscripts.com/ws_types.html" rel="nofollow">types</a>/<a href="http://www.ancientscripts.com/ws_families.html" class="external text" title="http://www.ancientscripts.com/ws_families.html" rel="nofollow">families</a>/<a href="http://www.ancientscripts.com/ws_regions.html" class="external text" title="http://www.ancientscripts.com/ws_regions.html" rel="nofollow">regions</a>/<a href="http://www.ancientscripts.com/ws_timeline.html" class="external text" title="http://www.ancientscripts.com/ws_timeline.html" rel="nofollow">timeline</a>/<a href="http://www.ancientscripts.com/ws_atoz.html" class="external text" title="http://www.ancientscripts.com/ws_atoz.html" rel="nofollow">A to Z</a>)</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Michael_Everson" title="Michael Everson">Michael Everson</a>'s <a href="http://www.evertype.com/alphabets/index.html" class="external text" title="http://www.evertype.com/alphabets/index.html" rel="nofollow">Alphabets of Europe</a></li>
<li><a href="http://scriptorium.17.forumer.com/index.php" class="external text" title="http://scriptorium.17.forumer.com/index.php" rel="nofollow">Scriptorium Bulletin Board</a>&#160;– A forum devoted to writing systems</li>
<li><a href="http://copper.chem.ucla.edu/~jericks" class="external text" title="http://copper.chem.ucla.edu/~jericks" rel="nofollow">Deseret Alphabet</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.protoalphabet.com/index.html" class="external text" title="http://www.protoalphabet.com/index.html" rel="nofollow">Alphabet &amp; protoalphabet the manifest of astrologic doctrine?</a></li>
</ul>
